title: Was ‘Proud Boy’ Rob Cantrell Seen Screaming at Cop at Anti-Lockdown Protest?
subtitle: A photograph truly shows a man screaming near an officer during an anti-lockdown protest.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A photograph shows Rob Cantrell, a member of the far-right group Proud Boys, screaming at an officer during an anti-lockdown protest in Michigan.
